: null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1020815, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 1, "EnglishDescription": "For the payment of debt and increase in sustenance the ritual of YAA WAHHAA-BO has been tried and tested. The ritual (amal) is that on Thursday or Friday recite 100 times salawaat the recite 2 rakat namaz in such a way that in each rakat after <Surah Fateha> recite <Aayatul Kursi> 15 times and <Surah Ikhlaas> 25 times. After namaz recites YAA WAHHAA-BO 41000 times without speaking till this ritual (amal) is completed. Senior scholars say that this ritual has been experienced and that his dua will be accepted.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Qarz ki adaayegi aur rizq mein izaafe ke liye YAA WAHHAA-BO ke vird ka amal bohot hi mujarrab (aazmaayi huwi) hai. Is ke amal ka tareeqa yeh hai keh Thursday ya Friday ke roz 100 martaba durood padhe phir 2 rakat namaz is tarah padhe keh us ki har rakat mein <Surah Fateha> ke baad 15 martaba <Aayatul Kursi> aur 25 maratab <Surah Ikhlaas> padhe. Namaz ke baad 41000 martaba YAA WAHHAA-BO ka vird pura karne se pehle kisi se koi kalaam (baat) na kare. Buzurg ulema ka kehna hai keh yeh amal tajurba kiya huwa hai keh us ki dua zaroor qabool hogi.", "UrduDescription": "قرض کی ادائیگی اور وسعت رزق کے لئے ’’یَا وَھَّابُ‘‘  کے ورد کا عمل بہت ہی مجرب ہے۔ اس کے عمل کا طریقہ یہ ہے کہ جمعرات یا جمعہ کے روز 100 مرتبہ درود شریف پڑھے پھر ۲ رکعت نماز اس طرح پڑھے کہ اس کی ہر رکعت میں <سورۂ فاتحہ> کے بعد 15 مرتبہ <آیت الکرسی> اور 25 مرتبہ <سورۂ اخلاص> پڑھے۔ سلام کے بعد 41000 مرتبہ اس اسم کا ورد کرے، ورد کی تکمیل سے پہلے کسی سے کوئی کلام نہ کرے۔ بزرگ علما کا کہنا ہے کہ یہ عمل تجربہ شدہ ہے کہ اس کی دعا ضرور قبول ہوگی۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4